org.bytedeco.javacpp

Class avfilter.AVFilterBufferRefAudioProps

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.avfilter.AVFilterBufferRefAudioProps
  • Enclosing class:
    avfilter

    public static class avfilter.AVFilterBufferRefAudioProps
extends Pointer
    Audio specific properties in a reference to an AVFilterBuffer. Since AVFilterBufferRef is common to different media formats, audio specific per reference properties must be separated out.
